      'cmgb2sfhg000arohmubsei6ar', 'wes-streeting-twitterx-statement-7-october-2023', 'Wes Streeting - Twitter/X Statement (7 October 2023)', 'Wes Streeting made this statement following the Hamas attacks on Israel on 7 October 2023. As a prominent Labour MP and Shadow Health Secretary, his response was part of broader political reactions to the escalating conflict. Streeting has been a consistent supporter of Israel''s right to exist and defend itself while also advocating for Palestinian rights.', 'Wes Streeting made this statement following the Hamas attacks on Israel on 7 October 2023. As a prominent Labour MP and Shadow Health Secretary, his response was part of broader political reactions to the escalating conflict. Streeting has been a consistent supporter of Israel''s right to exist and defend itself while also advocating for Palestinian rights.

