      'cmgb2ure0000aror65ps8n7p8', 'suella-braverman-sky-news-television-interview-statement-13-november-2023', 'Suella Braverman - Sky News Television Interview Statement (13 November 2023)', 'Following the October 7 Hamas attack on Israel and subsequent Israeli military response in Gaza, pro-Palestinian marches were taking place across the UK. Braverman made these comments during a Sky News interview, expressing concerns about rising antisemitic incidents and calling for an end to pro-Palestinian demonstrations.', 'Following the October 7 Hamas attack on Israel and subsequent Israeli military response in Gaza, pro-Palestinian marches were taking place across the UK. Braverman made these comments during a Sky News interview, expressing concerns about rising antisemitic incidents and calling for an end to pro-Palestinian demonstrations.

