      'cmgb38oca000drobyg4zuigtt', 'alexandria-ocasio-cortez-twitter-statement-17-may-2021', 'Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez - Twitter Statement (17 May 2021)', 'During the May 2021 escalation in Gaza, AOC made this statement via Twitter following Israeli airstrikes in Gaza and Hamas rocket attacks. The conflict had intensified after tensions in Jerusalem, particularly around Sheikh Jarrah evictions and Al-Aqsa Mosque incidents. Her statement came as progressive Democrats increasingly criticized U.S. military aid to Israel during active hostilities.', 'During the May 2021 escalation in Gaza, AOC made this statement via Twitter following Israeli airstrikes in Gaza and Hamas rocket attacks. The conflict had intensified after tensions in Jerusalem, particularly around Sheikh Jarrah evictions and Al-Aqsa Mosque incidents. Her statement came as progressive Democrats increasingly criticized U.S. military aid to Israel during active hostilities.

