      'cmgb2f6se000frolvcjw6i6j5', 'The scale of the problem was also dramatically overstated for political reasons by our opponents inside and outside the party, as well as by much of the media.', 'Jeremy Corbyn made this statement in response to the Equality and Human Rights Commission (EHRC) report that found the Labour Party had unlawfully harassed and discriminated against Jewish people under his leadership. The report concluded there had been serious failings in leadership and inadequate processes for handling antisemitism complaints during Corbyn''s tenure as party leader.', 'ORIGINAL', '2020-10-30T00:00:00.000Z',
