      'cmgb2fp29000frooc7594bb03', 'I am horrified by the slaughter of innocent Israelis by Hamas terrorists. Nothing justifies these acts of violence. Israel has the right to defend itself. Hamas must release all hostages and stop these attacks immediately.', 'Starmer made this statement following Hamas''s surprise attack on Israel on 7 October 2023, which killed over 1,400 Israelis. As Leader of the Opposition, he was responding to one of the most significant escalations in the Israeli-Palestinian conflict in decades. The statement was made as part of Labour''s official response to the crisis.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-10T23:00:00.000Z',
