      'cmgb2l7i1000crogcqryf9gjd', 'I would suspend arms sales to Israel. I would review our diplomatic relationship and I would look at sanctions as well.', 'During the Labour Party leadership contest, Lisa Nandy was asked at a hustings event about her stance on Israel-Palestine. She was responding to questions about what actions she would take as Labour leader regarding the Israeli-Palestinian conflict, particularly in light of concerns about human rights violations in occupied territories.', 'ORIGINAL', '2020-02-22T00:00:00.000Z',
