      'cmgb2o418000cro15wbpyl59q', 'Gaza is experiencing a genocide. The world is watching. History will judge us all.', 'Kate Osamor posted this statement on social media on Holocaust Memorial Day, which commemorates the victims of the Holocaust and other genocides. The timing was particularly sensitive as it coincided with the international day of remembrance for Holocaust victims. This occurred during the ongoing Israel-Gaza conflict that began in October 2023 following Hamas attacks on Israel and Israel''s subsequent military response in Gaza.', 'ORIGINAL', '2024-01-24T00:00:00.000Z',
