      'cmgb2pjpq000fro6m8ry3g77k', 'The killing of civilians, including children, is always wrong - whether Palestinian or Israeli. But we cannot ignore the asymmetry of power here. Israel is the occupying force with one of the world''s most advanced militaries. Palestinians in Gaza live under blockade.', 'During escalating violence between Israel and Hamas in May 2021, following tensions in East Jerusalem and Sheikh Jarrah, Lewis made this statement on Twitter calling for an end to violence while highlighting the power imbalance between Israel and Palestinians. This was part of broader international condemnation of civilian casualties during the 11-day conflict.', 'ORIGINAL', '2021-05-11T23:00:00.000Z',
