      'cmgb2zgl2000crobm9lgefh9f', 'I stand with Israel and its right to defend itself. The barbaric terrorist attacks by Hamas must be condemned in the strongest possible terms. My thoughts are with all those affected by this violence.', 'Following the 7 October 2023 Hamas attacks on Israel and the subsequent Israeli military response, many UK MPs made public statements regarding the conflict. Williamson posted this statement on social media as part of the broader political response to the escalating situation in Gaza and Israel.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-26T23:00:00.000Z',
