      'cmgb2zwy7000froddszx76tt0', 'Israel has every right to defend itself against the barbaric attacks by Hamas. We must stand with our democratic ally in the Middle East and support their right to exist and defend their people.', 'Following the October 7, 2023 Hamas attacks on Israel, Rees-Mogg made multiple statements supporting Israel''s right to defend itself during parliamentary debates and on social media. This particular statement was made during a House of Commons debate on the UK''s response to the Israel-Hamas conflict, where he expressed strong support for Israel''s military response and criticized those calling for immediate ceasefire.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-12-12T00:00:00.000Z',
