      'cmgb30se1000croh8sta0bchv', 'Israel has every right to defend itself against these barbaric attacks. Hamas is a terrorist organisation that deliberately targets civilians. The international community must stand with Israel in condemning these heinous acts of terrorism.', 'Following the major Hamas attack on Israel on 7 October 2023, which resulted in over 1,400 Israeli deaths and the taking of hostages, Duncan Smith issued a statement expressing solidarity with Israel and condemning the attacks as terrorism.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-06T23:00:00.000Z',
