      'cmgb33on2000crouctfzvz498', 'Solidarity with the people of Palestine. The international community cannot continue to stand by and watch as Palestinian families are forced from their homes and killed. This is a violation of international law and human rights. We must act.', 'During the escalation of violence in Gaza and Israel in May 2021, following tensions in East Jerusalem over planned evictions in Sheikh Jarrah neighborhood and clashes at Al-Aqsa Mosque, Mhairi Black posted a statement expressing solidarity with Palestinians on social media as part of widespread international reaction to the conflict.', 'ORIGINAL', '2021-05-14T23:00:00.000Z',
