      'cmgb35yxz000fro46gelai0n8', 'Israel has no right to defend itself from people whose land it occupies. That''s not self defence, that''s perpetuating occupation.', 'Following the Hamas attack on Israel on 7 October 2023, Yaqoob posted this statement on social media as part of her commentary on the Israeli-Palestinian conflict and Israel''s military response to the attacks.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-06T23:00:00.000Z',
