      'cmgb3a92b000froi5m6n35dse', 'The fighting must end. Palestinians deserve the same freedom and security as Israelis. We cannot be silent about the killing of children - Palestinian or Israeli. @POTUS must lead international efforts to end this violence and ensure accountability for these violations of human rights and international law.', 'Representative Pressley made this statement during the May 2021 escalation of violence between Israel and Hamas in Gaza. The 11-day conflict resulted in over 250 deaths, including many civilians and children on both sides. Pressley, along with other progressive Democrats, called for a more balanced U.S. approach to the conflict and criticized unconditional U.S. support for Israel.', 'ORIGINAL', '2021-05-20T23:00:00.000Z',
