      'cmgb3baz7000frologed7yort', 'I condemn Hamas'' attack on Israel in the strongest possible terms. The targeting of civilians is unacceptable. At the same time, I continue to support Palestinian human rights and self-determination. We need a ceasefire and de-escalation to prevent further loss of innocent life.', 'Following Hamas''s surprise attack on Israel on October 7, 2023, which killed over 1,200 Israelis and took hundreds hostage, Bowman issued statements attempting to balance condemnation of Hamas with continued support for Palestinian rights. His response was part of broader political pressure on progressive Democrats to respond to the crisis.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-06T23:00:00.000Z',
      'Official Congressional statement and social media', true, true, false,
      true, 'AIPAC spent over $14 million supporting his primary challenger George Latimer, making it the most expensive House primary in history. Bowman lost the June 2024 primary by 17 percentage points.',
