      'cmgb3cakz000fropmg4u28a4l', 'Israel must stop blocking humanitarian aid and allow it to reach the starving Palestinian people. As I''ve said before, we must end this war, secure the release of all hostages, and stop U.S. military aid that''s enabling the killing of so many innocent people, including aid workers trying to help.', 'Representative Casar made this statement on Twitter/X amid ongoing conflict in Gaza and reports of humanitarian aid being blocked from reaching Palestinian civilians. This was part of his broader criticism of U.S. military aid to Israel during the Gaza conflict.', 'ORIGINAL', '2024-05-10T23:00:00.000Z',
