      'cmgb3e84k000frowjrh5eewq5', 'Israel has a right to defend itself and we stand with our democratic ally. Hamas is a terrorist organization that must be held accountable for the October 7th attacks. At the same time, we must work to protect innocent Palestinian civilians and support a path toward a two-state solution that ensures security and dignity for both Israelis and Palestinians.', 'Following the October 7, 2023 Hamas attacks on Israel and Israel''s subsequent military response, many U.S. lawmakers issued statements expressing their positions on the conflict. Swalwell made this statement as part of the broader congressional response to the escalating violence.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-24T23:00:00.000Z',
