      'cmgb3epb7000iroyazl11ajzn', 'Hamas''s horrific terrorist attacks on innocent Israeli civilians constitute crimes against humanity. I condemn these attacks in the strongest possible terms and stand with Israel in its right to defend itself against terrorism. At the same time, we must work to protect innocent Palestinian civilians who are also suffering in this conflict.', 'Following the Hamas attack on Israel on October 7, 2023, Rep. Raskin issued a statement condemning the terrorist attacks while also expressing concern for Palestinian civilians. This was part of broader Congressional responses to the escalating conflict in Gaza and Israel.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-06T23:00:00.000Z',
