      'cmgb3g31b000cro4b7nox1fyg', 'Israel has a right to defend itself against rocket attacks from Hamas and other terrorist organizations. At the same time, we must work toward a just and lasting peace that recognizes the legitimate aspirations of both Israelis and Palestinians.', 'During the May 2021 escalation between Israel and Hamas in Gaza, Hoyer released this statement as part of his response to the conflict that resulted in civilian casualties on both sides. The statement came amid renewed violence that began after tensions in East Jerusalem and the Sheikh Jarrah neighborhood.', 'ORIGINAL', '2021-05-12T23:00:00.000Z',
