      'cmgb3nd0w000crovw5u0rlimi', 'California stands with Israel and condemns the unprovoked terrorist attacks by Hamas. We mourn the innocent lives lost and stand in solidarity with the Israeli people during this difficult time.', 'Governor Newsom issued this statement on social media following the Hamas attacks on Israel that began on October 7, 2023. The attacks involved rocket barrages and ground incursions that killed over 1,400 Israelis and took hundreds of hostages. Newsom''s statement was part of immediate responses from U.S. political leaders condemning the attacks.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-06T23:00:00.000Z',
