      'cmgb3p6jf000fro2ts669izne', 'I have determined that it is time to officially recognize Jerusalem as the capital of Israel. While previous presidents have made this a major campaign promise, they failed to deliver. Today, I am delivering.', 'President Trump announced his decision to formally recognize Jerusalem as Israel''s capital and move the U.S. embassy from Tel Aviv to Jerusalem, breaking with decades of U.S. policy. This decision fulfilled a campaign promise and implemented the Jerusalem Embassy Act of 1995, which previous presidents had repeatedly waived.', 'ORIGINAL', '2017-12-06T00:00:00.000Z',
