      'cmgb3tl6p000croj0umh6d6du', 'The United States must stand with our democratic ally Israel as it defends itself against these unprovoked attacks. Hamas is a terrorist organization, and Israel has every right to defend its people and its sovereignty.', 'Following Hamas''s surprise attack on Israel on October 7, 2023, which killed over 1,400 Israelis, McConnell issued a statement strongly supporting Israel''s right to defend itself. This came amid intense fighting and Israel''s military response in Gaza. McConnell has been a consistent supporter of U.S.-Israel relations throughout his Senate career and has regularly supported military aid packages to Israel.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-10T23:00:00.000Z',
