      'cmgb86967000crogws519isu3', 'What''s happening in the Gaza Strip isn''t a war, it''s a genocide. It''s not a war of soldiers against soldiers. It''s a war between a highly prepared army and women and children.', 'During an African Union summit in Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, President Lula made these comments comparing Israel''s military actions in Gaza to genocide. The remarks came amid the ongoing conflict between Israel and Hamas that began in October 2023, with Lula criticizing Israel''s military response in Gaza following Hamas''s attack on Israel.', 'ORIGINAL', '2024-02-28T00:00:00.000Z',
