      'cmgbd3c7z000croki5xc99gvw', 'The truth is that there is an obvious, undeniable, and hugely consequential moral difference between Israel and her enemies. Israel is a democracy that has always aspired to minimize casualties among civilians. Hamas and the other terrorist organizations arrayed against her are theocratic death cults that actively maximize the suffering of innocents—on both sides.', 'Harris published a blog post titled "Why Don''t I Criticize Israel?" during the 2014 Gaza War (Operation Protective Edge). The conflict had resulted in significant civilian casualties, and there was intense international debate about Israel''s military actions in Gaza. Harris wrote the piece to explain his position on Israel and address criticism that he was biased in favor of Israel.', 'ORIGINAL', '2014-07-26T23:00:00.000Z',
