      'cmgbdbnh1000croaxa31clz8h', 'Tonight, we begin with a Fox News alert. Israel is under attack. Hamas terrorists have launched a coordinated surprise assault against the Jewish state. Rockets are raining down on Israeli cities. Terrorists have infiltrated Israeli communities, going door to door, murdering innocent men, women, and children. This is evil incarnate.', 'Sean Hannity opened his Fox News show on October 7, 2023, addressing the Hamas attack on Israel that had occurred earlier that day. The attack marked the beginning of what would become the Israel-Gaza war, with Hamas launching a surprise assault involving rockets and ground infiltration into Israeli territory.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-06T23:00:00.000Z',
