      'cmgbdgjxy000froqcnepcd3wz', '22 dead - number rising. Schofield. Don''t you even dare. Do not be part of the problem. We need a final solution', 'This tweet was posted by Hopkins in the immediate aftermath of the Manchester Arena bombing on 22 May 2017, which killed 22 people and injured many more. The attack occurred after an Ariana Grande concert and was carried out by a suicide bomber. Hopkins appeared to be responding to what she perceived as insufficient responses to terrorism, though the specific reference to "Schofield" was unclear. The phrase "final solution" is historically associated with Nazi Germany''s plan for the genocide of European Jews.', 'ORIGINAL', '2017-05-21T23:00:00.000Z',
