      'cmgbdhb8e000cros69s9u2pqu', 'Israel is engaged in the collective punishment of Palestinians. The killing of civilians - including children - and the destruction of civilian infrastructure including media buildings is a war crime. Those cheering this on have lost their humanity.', 'This statement was made during the May 2021 escalation in Gaza, following clashes at Al-Aqsa Mosque and rocket exchanges between Hamas and Israel. The Israeli military had conducted airstrikes on Gaza, including the destruction of a building housing AP and Al Jazeera offices, which Israel claimed contained Hamas military intelligence assets.', 'ORIGINAL', '2021-05-11T23:00:00.000Z',
