      'cmgbdlnn0000fro951w15olro', 'The usual Israeli procedure is, whatever the pretext, to use disproportionate force to carry out plenty of crimes—war crimes—and to try to destroy the will to resist.', 'During the May 2021 escalation between Israel and Hamas in Gaza, Chomsky gave an interview to Democracy Now! discussing the conflict. This came after days of violence that began with tensions in East Jerusalem over evictions in Sheikh Jarrah and clashes at Al-Aqsa Mosque, leading to rocket fire from Gaza and Israeli airstrikes.', 'ORIGINAL', '2021-05-18T23:00:00.000Z',
