      'cmgbdvzp9000cro4q1bpfe02y', 'The Jewish lobby is extraordinary powerful here and particularly in the industry that I work in, the music industry and in rock ''n'' roll as they like to call it... I''ve been accused of being a Nazi and an antisemite for the last 10 years, which I am not.', 'Waters made these comments during a lengthy podcast interview discussing his political activism, the BDS movement, and criticism he has faced for his positions on Israel. The interview covered his views on the Israeli-Palestinian conflict and his response to accusations of antisemitism that have followed him for years.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-02-12T00:00:00.000Z',
