      'cmgbhsu17000iro1298ag734x', 'What''s happening in the Gaza Strip isn''t a war, it''s a genocide. It''s not a war of soldiers against soldiers. It''s a war between a highly prepared army and women and children.', 'During an African Union summit in Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, Lula made these remarks while discussing the ongoing Israel-Gaza conflict that began in October 2023 following Hamas attacks on Israel. His comments came during a period of international debate over Israel''s military response in Gaza and rising civilian casualties.', 'ORIGINAL', '2024-02-15T00:00:00.000Z',
