      'cmgbhws9t000frontr99jo6vr', 'The massacre of civilians in Gaza is unacceptable. The Israeli government''s response goes beyond legitimate defense and constitutes collective punishment of the Palestinian people. Brazil must position itself firmly for peace and human rights.', 'Following the escalation of violence between Israel and Hamas in October 2023, Boulos made this statement as part of a broader response by Brazilian left-wing politicians calling for an end to hostilities and criticizing Israel''s military response in Gaza.', 'ORIGINAL', '2023-10-11T23:00:00.000Z',
