      'resp_cmgbi3k9g000nrobx2s1gffp7', '*"We regret the one-sided position that ignores the terrorist attacks launched against Israeli civilians and the right of Israel to defend itself."*', 'RESPONSE', 'CRITICISM', '2021-05-12T23:00:00.000Z',
